blog.name: teesh-oh
blog.title: The Adventures of Cupcake Girl
blog.description:
I'm Teesh, a 24-year-old girl living a life of big and small adventures. I have fed my friends so many baked goods, even my second degree acquaintances refer to me as 'the cupcake girl'.

I document both of my dogs' life in photos, rant about inaccurate film adaptations of my favorite books and my real life nightmare is getting stuck in Manila traffic on rainy days. I plan to spend the rest of my time (and hard earned money) seeing the rest of the world, eating as much as I can without getting fat (hopefully), concocting sweets, and writing about it in between. My current goal is to win the lottery.

title: Japan 2018 || #ReputationTourTokyo & spending 8 days in Japan
body:
Japan 2018 || #ReputationTourTokyo & spending 8 days in Japan

I tend to write separate posts for every single day I’m on vacation in order to completely exhaust the memories I made at the time, and document them as detailed as possible.
